'''奇怪電波圓環'''<ref>{{cite news |title=天文學家震驚！ 宇宙中出現4個從未發現過的物體 |url=https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3224368 |date=2020-07-10 |work=[[自由時報|自由時報]] |accessdate=2020-07-16 |archive-date=2020-07-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200716192145/https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3224368 |dead-url=no }}</ref>（{{lang-en|Odd radio circle}}，簡稱'''ORC'''），又譯作'''無線電怪圈'''<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/22/5/18/n13739537.htm |title=天文學家發現神祕環形天體 或為星際間產物 |newspaper=[[大纪元时报|大纪元时报]] |date=2022-05-18 |access-date=2022-05-19 |language=zh-hant |archive-date=2022-05-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220521145359/https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/22/5/18/n13739537.htm }}</ref>，是[[天文學|天文學]]上一種暫時未能解釋的巨大天體，其在[[無線電波|無線電波]]長下看似是圓狀且邊緣明亮。截至2020年6月26日，天文學家已觀測到四個這樣的物體（可能還有六個）<ref name="ARX-20200726">{{cite journal |author=Norris, Ray P. |display-authors=et al. |title=Unexpected Circular Radio Objects at High Galactic Latitude |url=https://arxiv.org/abs/2006.14805 |date=2020-06-26 |journal=[[arxiv|arxiv]] |arxiv=2006.14805v1 |accessdate=2020-07-09 |archive-date=2020-07-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200708192619/https://arxiv.org/abs/2006.14805 |dead-url=no }}Note: submitted to the journal Nature Astronomy</ref><ref name="LS-20200709">{{cite news |last=Johnson-Groh |first=Mara |title=4 mysterious objects spotted in deep space are unlike anything ever seen |url=https://www.livescience.com/circular-radio-objects-space.html |date=2020-07-08 |work=Live Science |accessdate=2020-07-09 |archive-date=2020-07-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200709043520/https://www.livescience.com/circular-radio-objects-space.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="NS-20200703">{{cite news |last=Murugesu |first=Jason Arunn |title=Circles in space made of radio waves are like nothing we've ever seen |url=https://www.newscientist.com/article/2247978-circles-in-space-made-of-radio-waves-are-like-nothing-weve-ever-seen/ |date=2020-07-03 |work=[[New_Scientist|New Scientist]] |accessdate=2020-07-09 |archive-date=2020-07-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200708183312/https://www.newscientist.com/article/2247978-circles-in-space-made-of-radio-waves-are-like-nothing-weve-ever-seen/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="SA-20200709">{{cite news |last=Starr |first=Michelle |title=Astronomers Detect Unexpected Class of Mysterious Circular Objects in Space |url=https://www.sciencealert.com/mysterious-unidentified-circles-have-been-found-in-space |date=2020-07-09 |work=ScienceAlert.com |accessdate=2020-07-09 |archive-date=2020-07-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200709210958/https://www.sciencealert.com/mysterious-unidentified-circles-have-been-found-in-space |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="NW-20200709">{{cite news |last=Osborne |first=Hannah |title='Odd' Circles of Radio Waves Coming from Unknown Cosmic Source Discovered |url=https://www.newsweek.com/circle-radio-waves-space-source-unknown-1516549 |date=2020-07-09 |work=[[Newsweek|Newsweek]] |accessdate=2020-07-10 |archive-date=2020-07-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200709150825/https://www.newsweek.com/circle-radio-waves-space-source-unknown-1516549 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="VICE-20200710">{{cite news |last=Ferreira |first=Becky |title=Scientists Discover Unexplained Glowing Circles of Energy in Space - Scientists believe they have likely discovered a new and unexplained class of space object: the Odd Radio Circle, or ORC. |url=https://www.vice.com/en_us/article/qj4z8w/scientists-discover-unexplained-glowing-circles-of-energy-in-space |date=2020-07-10 |work=[[Vice_(雜誌)|Vice]] |accessdate=2020-07-11 |archive-date=2020-07-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200711033706/https://www.vice.com/en_us/article/qj4z8w/scientists-discover-unexplained-glowing-circles-of-energy-in-space |dead-url=no }}</ref>。已發現的奇怪電波圓環在無線電波長下非常明亮，但在[[可見光|可見光]]、[[紅外線|紅外]]或[[X射線|X射線]][[波長|波長]]下則不可見<ref name="ARX-20200726" /><ref name="LS-20200709" />。其中兩個奇怪電波圓環的中心觀察到有星系的存在，說明ORC可能是由星系演化而成<ref name="LS-20200709" />。

== 描述 ==
奇怪電波圓環是在2019年末，於[[澳大利亚平方千米阵探路者|澳大利亚平方千米阵探路者]]的{{link-en|宇宙進化圖計劃|Evolutionary Map of the Universe}}[[前導實驗|前導實驗]]中被發現的<ref name="ARX-20200726"/>。所有觀測到的ORC直徑約為1[[弧分|弧分]]，處於[[銀道坐標系|高銀緯]]，距[[銀河平面|銀河平面]]有一定距離。圓環的成因不明，有可能是球狀[[激波|激波]]、[[快速電波爆發|快速電波爆發]]、[[伽瑪射線暴|伽瑪射線暴]]或[[中子星碰撞|中子星碰撞]]。研究人員認為由於ORC擁有大[[角直徑|角直徑]]的關係，如果與這四項相關的話，那麼它必定有著非常大的[[紅移|紅移]]，為宇宙中最遙遠且古老的天體之一。與此同時也存在著{{link-en|資料偽缺陷|Artifact (error)}}、[[校準|校準]]誤差或[[反捲積|反捲積]]的可能性。但研究人員偏向相信奇怪電波圓環是一種新的[[天體|天體]]<ref name="SA-20200709" />。研究員又指圓狀在射電天文圖像中非常普遍，通常代表球狀天體，例如[[超新星殘骸|超新星殘骸]]、[[行星狀星雲|行星狀星雲]]、[[星周包層|星周包層]]或諸如[[原行星盤|原行星盤]]等[[吸積盤|吸積盤]]<ref name="SA-20200709" />。

